column14: SEEL new note from Roth today As outlined in our SEEL initiation suicidality is a looming public health crisis with staggering prevalence numbers substantially higher than we expected In this report we provide an uptodate estimation of the market opportunity and reasons why we continue to believe SLS005 is set for successWith hospitalization rates after ER visits for suicidality at the 40 mark the market opportunity for SLS002 is larger than previously thought
